{"tid":519752,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"一高轉轉波就會掃牙","createTime":"2018-01-04T16:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T01:15:24.000Z","uid":91332,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"86ee382b20b380bfb3002888ac83df516e7032ab","tid":519752,"uid":91332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"小弟買左架ek3棍仔，唔知點解架車一過3000轉到轉波就會掃牙，如果太高轉就要踩住極力子兩三秒之後放先唔會掃牙<br />\n另外仲有有時一波會卡實左轉唔波，搞到依家揸得仲慢過隻龜，唔知有冇ching可以話我知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfeb848ac87ac60d833b015601992d5e093bc410","tid":519752,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"打散波箱換銅索牙 <br />\n不過普通操車用 ek3 就有佢啦<br />\n整仲貴過部車"},{"pid":"8d78f3bf933c495e0174e6b022ddc741a06b45c5","tid":519752,"uid":8060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"渣多排劏左佢算喇"},{"pid":"53e4850a7a767593702cd8b23202cc2329cc9332","tid":519752,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T22:47:30.000Z","msg":"整貴過架車，劏算"},{"pid":"d40e98a593581613a3ab33b8c22ae27dd85c234f","tid":519752,"uid":72751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T00:42:36.000Z","msg":"銅索牙到期<br />\n料平人工貴"},{"pid":"1e255f7d612973179b4e67679f7fd5ceb5c73895","tid":519752,"uid":1623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:02:31.000Z","msg":"試下換波箱油"},{"pid":"8e1bc6b66842c09d3124230a5322e878fa489634","tid":519752,"uid":12523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"換左極力子先啦"},{"pid":"983cb957d136027da11d93f07efda29a4775b6cd","tid":519752,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"唔岩聽既說話 你想唔想聽"},{"pid":"829492fcf3deb8723848b0909151d1205d47d87c","tid":519752,"uid